Commentary: |
  The same in Japanese Zen, yukezammai=samsidhi in which all activity is
  play (lila), or 'the samadhi of play’.
    Cf:
      By: R. Kita and K. Nagaya
      Title: How Altruism Is Cultivated in Zen
      Page: 135
---
Thou didst contrive this 'I' and ‘we’ in order that Thou mightst play the game
of worship with Thyself,

That all 'I’s’ and ‘thou’s’ should become one soul and at last should be
submerged in the Beloved.
